headline: S&P Futures Tick Higher With U.S. Economic Data in Focus
summary: December S&P 500 E-Mini futures (ESZ25) are trending up +0.16% this morning as traders bet that a new round of U.S. economic data will reinforce expectations for a Federal Reserve rate cut next week.
